		routeInfo
				.add("a. Walk to Arc de Triomf Station from Ressidencia Onix\n"
						+ "b. Take L1 (red) train towards Hospital de Bellvitge and get off at Espanya\n"
						+ "c. Get off at Espanya and exit the station.");
